   in order to m aintain the wave pattern a continual supply of free energy is required.
   It is clear that this must be so since there is a continual degradation of energy through
   diffusion. This energy is supplied through the ‘ fuel substances ’ (A, B in the last example),
   which are degraded into ‘ waste products5 (D, E ) .
